# RFC-002 — System Architecture

**Status:** Accepted  
**Version:** 1.0.0  
**Author:** Atlas AI Founding Team  
**Date:** July 21, 2026

---

# 1. Purpose

This document defines the technical architecture of Atlas AI.

Its purpose is to ensure that every future product built by Atlas follows the same engineering principles, enabling scalability, maintainability, and long-term evolution.

The first implementation target is Atlas Immigration.

---

# 2. Architecture Philosophy

Atlas is not a single application.

Atlas is a platform.

Every future product must reuse the same core infrastructure.

Products should implement business rules while sharing authentication, AI services, storage, notifications, memory, and security.

---

